name: Gnome Outreach Program for Women 2013 - Mozilla Release Metrics Dashboard Project
body:
### First entry
11th December, 2012

Had a sleepless night and got up only to find the real announcement time to be at 6am tomorrow (8pm GMT) T_T Thankfully, Lukas(@lsblakk) sent me an email in the afternoon and I finally knew that I GOT IN! Anyway, I'll be jotting down anything related to my internship here. Looking forward to an invaluable experience and a helpful starting contribution towards the FOSS community!

### Contributors
Thanks to the GNOME OPW coordinators and Mozilla for organizing and sponsoring this wonderful program!
tagline: My experience as an OPW intern working on the Mozilla Release Metrics dashboard project
